---
---
<section data-step="3" class="step-panel hidden min-h-[calc(100vh-8rem)] px-4 py-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
  <div class="text-6xl mb-6">🎮</div>
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-fsinf-dark dark:text-fsinf-cream mb-3">
    Discord <span class="text-[#5865f2]">beitreten</span>
  </h2>
  <p class="text-fsinf-dark/60 dark:text-fsinf-cream/60 mb-8 max-w-md leading-relaxed">
    Unser Discord-Server ist der Ort für Gaming, AGs und informellen Austausch.
    Bestimmte Rollen wie die <strong class="text-fsinf-dark dark:text-fsinf-cream">LAN-Orga-Rolle</strong> werden
    ausschließlich über Discord vergeben.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-[#5865f2]/10 border border-[#5865f2]/30 rounded-2xl p-8 w-full max-w-sm mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 justify-center">
      <span class="text-2xl">🔊</span>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-fsinf-dark dark:text-fsinf-cream text-lg">FSINF-Server</h3>
    </div>
    <a
      id="discord-invite-link"
      href="#"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      data-auto-check="discord"
      class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full px-6 py-3 bg-[#5865f2] text-white font-semibold text-base rounded-xl hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
    >
      Discord beitreten
      <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
        <path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h6M15 3h6v6M10 14L21 3"/>
      </svg>
    </a>
  </div>

  <p class="text-sm text-fsinf-dark/40 dark:text-fsinf-cream/40">
    Sobald du beigetreten bist, wird der „Weiter"-Button aktiv ↓
  </p>
</section>
